Is this series worth reading?
Definitely worth reading. It's fun, well-written, and Stephanie is extremely relatable. Plus the team-ups/contributing characters are amazing: Oracle, Robin, Red Robin, Supergirl, Klarion, Squire, Proxy... It goes on.
